# Route checklist (`/Users/aldous/Desktop/todo.txt`)

Tracks ADS page reskin progress. One line per route; `[x]` = done, `[ ]` = not done.

## When to update

- **User approves a page** (e.g. "done", "approved", "looks good") → change that route's line to `[x]` in `todo.txt`.
- Do this in the same session when possible; keep the checklist current after explicit approval.

## Never do this

- Do **not** check routes off because implementation finished, tests passed, or you judge the page complete.
- Do **not** batch-check multiple routes unless the user explicitly approved each one.

## Matching routes

Find the line by path (e.g. `/bounced`, `/sign_up/cancel/`). Locale prefixes (`/es`, `/fr`) are optional — match the path segment in the checklist.
